<i>noun</i>: 유신 [유신], 개혁 [개ː혁], 개변 [개ː변] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>유신 [유신]</dt><br>
<dd>reformation; the Revitalizing Reform</dd><br>
<dd>낡은 제도나 체제를 고쳐 새롭게 함.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of correcting and renewing an old system or regime.</dd><br>
<dt>개혁 [개ː혁]</dt><br>
<dd>reform; reformation</dd><br>
<dd>불합리한 제도나 기구 등을 새롭게 고침.</dd><br>
<dd>Correcting irrational systems or institutions.</dd><br>
<dt>개변 [개ː변]</dt><br>
<dd>innovation; reformation; renovation</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 상태, 제도, 시설 등을 더 좋게 만들려고 고치거나 바꾸는 것.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of changing or altering to make better certain situations, systems and facilities.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>